  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2177",
  "title": "Increase limit of pagination above 100 pages of results, allow more than 1000 returned results.",
  "body": "So currently the pagination widget limits the max number of pages you can have at 100, and I guess this is because the limit of returned results using instantsearch.js is 1000 records.\r\n\r\nI would expect this to allow you to paginate through all the results in the index, or at least have this configurable.\r\n\r\nPerhaps a solution is after getting the first 1000, that then a query is done for the next 1000? ",
